          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Law Enforcement Retirement Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill broadens the definition of &quot;law enforcement officer&quot; for purposes of enhanced retirement benefits under the Federal Employees' Retirement System. </p> <p>Specifically, it includes, as a law enforcement officer, a member of the Capitol Police who transfers to a supervisory or administrative position with the Federal Law Enforcement Training Center. </p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2018-07-24</actionDate>
        </item>
